1
00:00:01,886 --> 00:00:02,886
What is it?

2
00:00:07,820 --> 00:00:10,620
Sire, I have bare news from the Italian
court.

3
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:12,320
There has... there has been a robbery.

4
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:14,280
What?

5
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:17,742
Apparently, Margrave
Yob's people... they freed

6
00:00:17,743 --> 00:00:20,300
the hostages and...
and stole all the silver.

7
00:00:20,820 --> 00:00:21,820
And vanished.

8
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:28,290
All our silver?

9
00:00:29,150 --> 00:00:29,830
All of it.

10
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:31,490
But... but that's not all.

11
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:35,552
Sire, word has come that
Yobst is mustering an army

12
00:00:35,553 --> 00:00:39,370
and is... is planning to go
to the aid of Kuttenberg.

13
00:00:41,339 --> 00:00:43,150
Our that treacherous little hall.

